{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sourceId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","text":"Feature","identifier":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature-swift.typealias"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"parameters":[{"name":"sourceId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The identifier of the style source.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source."}]}],"name":"features"},{"name":"dataId","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"kind":"parameters"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"and listen to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onSourceDataLoaded"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter to filter the events)","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"onMapLoadingError"},{"type":"text","text":" with "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"type = metadata"},{"text":" if data parsing error has occurred.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Partially updating a GeoJSON source is not compatible with using shared cache and generated IDs.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is important to ensure that every feature in the GeoJSON style source, as well as the newly added"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature, has a unique ID (or a unique promote ID if in use). Failure to provide unique IDs will result"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in a "},{"code":"map-loading-error","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"name":"Note","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The method allows the user to provide a data ID, which will be returned as the "},{"code":"dataId","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" parameter in the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" event. However, it’s important to note that multiple partial updates can be queued"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for the same GeoJSON source when ongoing source parsing is taking place. In these cases, the partial"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"updates will be applied to the source in batches. Only the data ID provided in the most recent call within"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"each batch will be included in the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"source-data-loaded"},{"text":" event. If no data ID is provided in the most recent","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"call, the data ID in the ","type":"text"},{"code":"source-data-loaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"event will be null."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"type":"aside","style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"Throws","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":""},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleError"},{"text":" if there is a problem adding features to the source.","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/mapboxmaps\/stylemanager\/addgeojsonsourcefeatures(forsourceid:features:dataid:)"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Add additional features to a GeoJSON style source."}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"method","modules":[{"name":"MapboxMaps"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","title":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","externalID":"s:10MapboxMaps12StyleManagerC24addGeoJSONSourceFeatures11forSourceId8features04dataK0ySS_Say4Turf7FeatureVGSSSgtF","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"forSourceId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"features"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Feature"},{"kind":"text","text":"], "},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"kind":"text","text":"?)"}],"role":"symbol"},"sections":[],"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/StyleManager\/addGeoJSONSourceFeatures(forSourceId:features:dataId:)","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps","doc:\/\/MapboxMa